I bring to you, quite possibly, my last surf map.
It took me about 6 months on and off working on this thing.

It contains 10 stages. Decent detail and size.
Edit : According to "Sacred91" the map difficulty is 2 and 3. So ... yeah.

The winner gets to choose various minigames and gets to choose to kill players by stage.
Map size is due to many custom textures and about 3 models.
